@model IEnumerable<HaarlemFilmFestival.Models.Jazz>

@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Jazz";
}
<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Visit Haarlem Jazz</h1>
    <p>
        Haarlem Jazz is an important music event for the City of Haarlem.
        During the Haarlem festival, we want to recreate part of this festival by inviting some of the bands that previously performed there to play at the Patronaat.
        On Sunday, some of the bands will taketo the big stage at the Grote Markt to perform for all visitors for free!
    </p>
    <p class="jazz1">See the artists and times below!</p>
        <div class="jazz">
            <p>
                Haarlem Jazz is one of the big jazz stages in The Netherlands! Various famous artists will be playing.
                All kinds of famous artists will be playing. Gare du Nord, Soul Six , Lilith Merlot and many more. If you want some standard dabbler tracks, you should definitely listen to Gare du Nord.
                But if you want a more special act, don’t forget Han Bennink! Haarlem Jazz will show Haarlem what they got!
                And last but not least, Sunday is free for all visitors! Come and visit the Grote Markt for free, and enjoy with other people.
                So what holds you back? Pick a ticket and add it to your shopping cart.
                <div class="jazzimage"><img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/Images/u1082-verkleindvoorwebsite.png")" /></div>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <h1>Tickets</h1>

    <table class="table">
        <tr>
            <th>
                @Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.Rang)
            </th>
            <th>
                @Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.Rangprijs)
            </th>
            <th>
                @Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.Band)
            </th>
            <th></th>
        </tr>

        @foreach (var item in Model)
        {
            <tr>
                <td>
                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Rang)
                </td>
                <td>
                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Rangprijs)
                </td>
                <td>
                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Band)
                </td>
                <td>
                    @Html.ActionLink("Add to cart", "Index", "Tickets")
                    @*"Add to cart", "Index", "Tickets", new { id = item.JazzId }*@
                </td>
            </tr>
        }

    </table>

    <h1>Line-up</h1>

    @foreach (var item in Model)
    {
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Band)</h2>
                <p>The Gumbo Kings are a Dutch supergroup that combines the groove of New Orleans Funk with the grittiness of Delta Blues and the melodies of Memphis Soul.</p>
                <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/Images/u1063.png")" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Band)</h2>
                <p>Gare du Nord has grown into a dazzling live band with the originally Italian singer Dorona Alberti as the shining center. Dorona is not only one of the best singers in the Netherlands; with her sexy live act she knows how to move everyone in the audience.</p>
                <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/Images/u1055-verkleindvoorwebsite.png")" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <h2>@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Band)</h2>
                <p>He has performed throughout the US and worldwide and forged a clear identity as a composer, arranger, and bandleader to match his powerful saxophonic voice.&nbsp; His latest release, Beloved, is his second album for the Truth Revolution Recording Collective.&nbsp; In the company of his working band Allen calls upon the musical language of McLean, Lester Young, Charlie Parker, Sonny Rollins, John Coltrane and others.</p>
                <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/Images/u1070-verkleindvoorwebsite.png")" />
            </div>
        </div>
    }
